source_text: 026<TAB>Insan inkuanen Jacob ed kinen Jose, Onung na sankanengneng mo, magano ak lan ompatey, balet mansiansian kaibam so Dios, tan papawilen to kad dalin na saray atateng mo.
target_text: 024<TAB>Maging dakal lang bansa ding lahi na.

source_text: 027<TAB>Diad sika, aliwan saray lalakin agagim, so pangitdan ko na Sikem, say mataban dalin a sinamsam kod saray Amorreo diad panamegley na ispadak tan panak.
target_text: 025<TAB>Binendisyunan na la ketang aldong ita.

source_text: <MISSING_TRANSLATION>
target_text: 025<TAB>Ngana, Gamitan de ring Israelita ing lagyu mu neng mamendisyun la.

source_text: <MISSING_TRANSLATION>
target_text: 025<TAB>Sabian da, Gawan na ko sana ning Dios a kalupa ra di Efraim at Manase.

source_text: <MISSING_TRANSLATION>
target_text: 025<TAB>Makanyan neng pepaygit Jacob i Efraim kang Manase.

source_text: <MISSING_TRANSLATION>
target_text: 026<TAB>Kanita nganang Jacob kang Jose, Anak, malapit na kung mate, oneng e na ka paburen ning Dios.

source_text: <MISSING_TRANSLATION>
target_text: 026<TAB>Ibalik na ka king gabun da ring kekang pipumpunan.

source_text: <MISSING_TRANSLATION>
target_text: 027<TAB>Metung pa, babie ke keka at e karing kapatad mu ing Sikem a simbut ku karing Amoreo kapamilatan na ning espada at pana.

source_text: verse<TAB>content
target_text: verse<TAB>content

source_text: 001<TAB>Impaawit nen Jacob iray anak ton lalaki tan kuanto, Gali diad abay ko, ta ibagak so nagawad sikayo diad arapen a panaon
target_text: 001<TAB>Inaus na lang Jacob ding anak na at ngana karela, Lumapit kayung makapadurut kanaku ban asabi ku kekayu ing malyari karing aldo daratang.

source_text: 002<TAB>Mantitipon tan dengel kayo,
target_text: 002<TAB>Lumapit kayu at makiramdam, O anak nang Jacob,

source_text: 003<TAB>lalakin anak nen Jacob,
target_text: 003<TAB>at pakiramdaman ye i Israel a tata yu.

source_text: 004<TAB>Dengel kayod ama yon Israel.
target_text: 004<TAB>Ika, Ruben, ing kakung pangane,

source_text: 005<TAB>Ruben ya anak kon pangulowan,
target_text: 005<TAB>ika ing kakung sikanan at mumuna nang bunga ning kakung pangalalaki,

source_text: 006<TAB>sikay biskeg ko,
target_text: 006<TAB>tutu kang kagalang-galang at mayupaya.

source_text: 007<TAB>Tan onaan ya anak ko nen kabisbiskegan ko,
target_text: 007<TAB>Mengari kang danum ning albug a lalagusgus,

source_text: 008<TAB>Say sankamapaatageyan tan sankabiskegan ed amin da ray anak kon lalaki.
target_text: 008<TAB>oneng aliwa ika ing mipaygit karing kapatad mu,

source_text: 009<TAB>Singa ka mabiskeg a delap,
target_text: 009<TAB>uling dinatan me ing pagkeran nang tata mu;

source_text: 010<TAB>Balet ag ka magmaliw a sankatalonggaringan,
target_text: 010<TAB>asawa na sipingnan me.

source_text: 011<TAB>Lapud akiakdul kad inamung kon bii,
target_text: 011<TAB>I Simeon at Levi mikapatad la,

source_text: 012<TAB>Tan dinotakan moy dokulan na amam.
target_text: 012<TAB>panampalasan da la ring pataram da.

source_text: 013<TAB>Sanagi ra di Simeon tan Levi.
target_text: 013<TAB>E ku tagunan ing pulung da

source_text: 014<TAB>Ikakana ray armas dad panggawa ray deral.
target_text: 014<TAB>o makiabe king dapat da.

source_text: 015<TAB>Ag ak mibalid maamut iran tongtongan da.
target_text: 015<TAB>Kabud mimua la, makamate la;

source_text: 016<TAB>Ag ak mibiang ed saray pandaragop da,
target_text: 016<TAB>potang makaratang la tula pati toro pipilayan da.

source_text: 017<TAB>Ta lapud petang na olo ra amatey iray totoo
target_text: 017<TAB>Isumpa ing mabangis dang mua,

source_text: 018<TAB>Tan nilopuy da ray bakan kalakyan a para galaw.
target_text: 018<TAB>antimu rin ing ugali dang mabagsik.

source_text: 019<TAB>Sakey a samba komuy niwala ed pasnuk da, lapud alablabas,
target_text: 019<TAB>Pangalat ku la king bansa nang Jacob,

source_text: 020<TAB>Tan diad petang na olo ra, lapud mapalalon maruksa.
target_text: 020<TAB>at isambulat king mabilug a Israel.

source_text: 021<TAB>Ikaykayat ko rad intiron dalin na Israel.
target_text: 021<TAB>Ika naman, Juda, purian da ka

source_text: 022<TAB>Itaytayak ko rad saray totoo na Israel.
target_text: 022<TAB>at duku la keka ding kapatad mu;

source_text: 023<TAB>Juda, idayew ka na saray agagim a lalaki.
target_text: 023<TAB>kalaban mu tatalnan mu la batal;

source_text: 024<TAB>Tetekmelan mod beklew iray kalaban mo.
target_text: 024<TAB>Juda, anti ka waring leon,

source_text: 025<TAB>Ondakmomod sika iray lalakin agagim.
target_text: 025<TAB>pasibayu kang sasalikut kaybat mung mekamate;

source_text: 026<TAB>Si Juda et singa lion.
target_text: 026<TAB>leon kang magpaynawa a e na lalapitan ning ninuman.

source_text: 027<TAB>Papateyen to ray labay ton pateyen, insan ompapawil ed balaung to.
target_text: 027<TAB>E ya mako misan man ing setro kang Juda

source_text: 028<TAB>Maninat-inat tan mandokul-dokul.
target_text: 028<TAB>ni ing simbulu ning kayupayan na.

source_text: 029<TAB>Anggapoy makakpel a manigensigen ed sikato.
target_text: 029<TAB>Angga king datang ya itang talan king setro mu

source_text: 030<TAB>Bembenan toy baston na ari.
target_text: 030<TAB>a sukat dang pamintuan ding tau.

source_text: 031<TAB>Manoley lawas iray kabyangay boleg to.
target_text: 031<TAB>Tatali ne ing asno na king tanaman ubas,

source_text: 032<TAB>Maniter ed sikato iray bansa na buis da
target_text: 032<TAB>king pun a tutung mepili;

source_text: 033<TAB>Tan ondakmomo ran ontoluk ed sikato.
target_text: 033<TAB>alak ing pamipi na karing imalan na,

source_text: 034<TAB>Isisinger tod sengeg na ubas so kilaw ya asno to,
target_text: 034<TAB>at ing balabal na king malutung sabo ubas.

source_text: 035<TAB>Isisinger tod sankaabigan ya ubas.
target_text: 035<TAB>Mata na malutu na la king lasing na,

source_text: 036<TAB>Ipepesak toy kawes to ed alak ya ambalangan singa dala.
target_text: 036<TAB>at ding ipan na maputi la king gatas a inuman na.

source_text: 037<TAB>Ombabalanga ray mata to lapud kakainom toy alak.
target_text: 037<TAB>Zebulun, manuknangan ka lele ning dagat;

source_text: 038<TAB>Ompopoti ray ngipen to lapud kakainom toy gatas.
target_text: 038<TAB>maging sadsaran kang barku,

source_text: 039<TAB>Si Zabulon et manayam ed gilig na dayat.
target_text: 039<TAB>miras ya ing gabun mu angga Sidon.

source_text: 040<TAB>Magmaliw a puirto na saray barko iray sakop ton gilig na dayat.
target_text: 040<TAB>Isacar, anti ka king metung a asnong masikan,

source_text: 041<TAB>Say dalin to onsabi ya anggad Sidon.
target_text: 041<TAB>sasalikut pilatan da ring kawan.

source_text: 042<TAB>Si Isacar et singa mabiskeg ya asno
target_text: 042<TAB>Panakit mu king masanting a pipagpaynawan, at king makayamang gabun,

source_text: 043<TAB>A mandokdokul ed leet na saray sapin a sako.
target_text: 043<TAB>beba mu na la ding pago mu ban mamusan at pa-ipus.

source_text: 044<TAB>Balet nanenengneng ton maung a pasen so pampapainawaan to
target_text: 044<TAB>Panimunan na lang Dan ding taung sakup na

source_text: 045<TAB>Tan makaroyroyo so dalin.
target_text: 045<TAB>anting metung karing tribu na ning Israel.

source_text: 046<TAB>Ipaparaan toy takeb ton manakbat
target_text: 046<TAB>Anti yang ubingan king lele ning dalan, kamamalu king pidadalanan;

source_text: 047<TAB>Tan sikatoy napapasoot a mankimey a sakey ya aripen.
target_text: 047<TAB>sakung ning kabayu tuktukan na ban anabu ne itang makasake.

source_text: 048<TAB>Si Dan et manoley ed saray totoo to.
target_text: 048<TAB>Ing kekang pamagligtas, O Ginu , kakung panenayan.

source_text: 049<TAB>Magmaliw iran singa saray arum a tribu na Israel.
target_text: 049<TAB>Salakayan de ring tulisan i Gad,

source_text: 050<TAB>Magmaliw ya oleg ed gilig na dalan si Dan,
target_text: 050<TAB>pero tagal ya at salakayan na la.

source_text: 051<TAB>Sakey a nanditan oleg diad gilig na basbas,
target_text: 051<TAB>Ing pupul nang Aser tutung dakal,

source_text: 052<TAB>A mangetket ed mokur na kabayo,
target_text: 052<TAB>pamangan karapatdapat karing aring marangal.

source_text: 053<TAB>Pian napelag a nabalongyar ed beneg to so akakabayo.
target_text: 053<TAB>Usa yang mebulus i Neftali;

source_text: 054<TAB>Manalagar ak na panangilaban mo, Katawan .
target_text: 054<TAB>masanting la ding maging anak na.

source_text: 055<TAB>Dogpaan na sakey ya olup na
target_text: 055<TAB>Asno yang malyap i Jose,

source_text: 056<TAB>matatakew si Gad,
target_text: 056<TAB>asnong malyap lele ning sibul;

source_text: 057<TAB>Balet poliktaran to ra, insan to ra osilan.
target_text: 057<TAB>malyap yang asno king libis ning bunduk.

source_text: 058<TAB>Panlapwan na masustansian tagano so dalin nen Aser.
target_text: 058<TAB>Penagal de ring mamana,

source_text: 059<TAB>Mangiter na kakanen a manepeg ed ari.
target_text: 059<TAB>pemana re at pepasakitan e makanyan-kanyan.

source_text: 060<TAB>Si Neftali et sakey ya ulsa a batik-batik ya anggan iner,
target_text: 060<TAB>Pero menatili yang makayabit ing pana na, at ding gamat na matatag la.

source_text: 061<TAB>Tan makapalikliket iray anak ton ankekelag.
target_text: 061<TAB>King saup ning Mayupayang Dios nang Jacob,

source_text: 062<TAB>Si Jose et singa sakey ya asnod katakelan a walad gilig na sobul,
target_text: 062<TAB>king lagyu ning Pastul a matibe nang Batu ning Israel.

source_text: 063<TAB>Sakey a kilaw na kabayo a walad alusadsar na palandey.
target_text: 063<TAB>Dios ning kekang tata, datang ya sa ban sumaup keka,

source_text: 064<TAB>Pinasyan dogpaan na saray kalaban to,
target_text: 064<TAB>bendisyunan na ka sa ning Dios a Mayupaya

source_text: 065<TAB>Tan osilan dan awit day pana ra.
target_text: 065<TAB>karing bendisyun a ibat king matas a banua,

source_text: 066<TAB>Balet mansiasiansian mabiskeg so pana to,
target_text: 066<TAB>bendisyun a ibat king kalalalaman,

source_text: 067<TAB>Tan napapabiskeg iray taklay to
target_text: 067<TAB>bendisyun a ibat karing salu at sepupunan.

source_text: 068<TAB>Diad panamegley na pakayari na Makapanyarin Dios nen Jacob.
target_text: 068<TAB>Ding bendisyun nang ibpa mu

source_text: 069<TAB>Napapabiskeg na Managpastol, say Manangyagel ed Israel.
target_text: 069<TAB>maygit la karing bendisyun ding pipumpunan ku,

source_text: 070<TAB>Say Dios na amam so ontutulong ed sika,
target_text: 070<TAB>mamabut la king alang anggang bunduk.

source_text: 071<TAB>Say Makapanyarin-amin a Dios a mamibindision ed sika,
target_text: 071<TAB>Mibie la sana kang Jose,

source_text: 072<TAB>Na saray bindision ya oran a manlalapud tawen
target_text: 072<TAB>king kanuan ning mipasubali karing kapatad na.

source_text: 073<TAB>Tan aralem iran sobul a manlalapud dalem na dalin,
target_text: 073<TAB>Asu yang gubat a mabangis i Benjamin;

source_text: 074<TAB>Saray bindision ya amayamay a baka tan amayamay ya anak,
target_text: 074<TAB>neng abak gigisanan ne ing kalaban;

source_text: 075<TAB>Saray bindision a trigo tan saray rosas,
target_text: 075<TAB>neng bengi naman pirakerakayan na ing banding mesamsam.

source_text: 076<TAB>Saray bindision a dagdaan iran palandey,
target_text: 076<TAB>Ila deti ring labing adua nang tribu ning Israel, at yan ing sinabi nang tata ra tungkul karela, kanitang memun ya karela at menabilin king metung at metung.

source_text: 077<TAB>Saray makapalikliket a bengatlan manlalapud andi-anggaan iran pokdul.
target_text: 077<TAB>Kaybat ngana karela, Malapit na kung makiabe karing kanakung pipumpunan.

source_text: 078<TAB>Mansiansia komun ira yan bindision ed olo nen Jose,
target_text: 077<TAB>Ikutkut yu ku at iyabe karing pipumpunan ku king kueba a atyu king marangle nang Efron a Hiteo.

source_text: 079<TAB>Diad muling na samay nibiig nen saman ed saray agagi ton lalaki.
target_text: 078<TAB>Atyu iting kueba king marangle karin Makpela, king dane aslagan ning Mamre, king sakup ning Canaan.

source_text: 080<TAB>Si Benjamin et singa sakey a maruksan asod katakelan.
target_text: 078<TAB>Seli neng Abraham iting marangle kang Efron a Hiteo bilang pikutkutan.

source_text: 081<TAB>Agew-labin mamangakan na napapatey to.
target_text: 079<TAB>Karin ya makakutkut i Abraham at i Sarah a asawa na, antimu rin i Isaac at i Rebeca a asawa na.

source_text: 082<TAB>Sikara yay labinduan tribu na Israel, tan sikara yay kaonuran a salita nen ama ra nen bindisionan toy balang sakey ed sikara.
target_text: 079<TAB>Karin kia naman pepakutkut i Lea.

source_text: 083<TAB>Insan ingganggan nen Jacob iray lalakin anak to, Natan ta magano ak lan mitipon ed saray totook ya andi lad bilay, kerewen kon ipompon yo ak ya ipitipon ed amak tan saray lalakik diad lobuk a walad alog nen Efron a Heteo,
target_text: 080<TAB>Mesali ya karing Hiteo ing marangle at ing kueba.

source_text: 084<TAB>diad Macpela a bokig na Mamre, diad dalin na Canaan.
target_text: 081<TAB>Kayari nang menabilin karing anak na, simpa na la king pagkeran ding bitis na, at saka ne mepatlud a inawa at mekiabe karing pipumpunan na.

source_text: 084<TAB>Sinaliw nen laki yon Abraham iman ya ongib tan alog ed kinen Efron a Heteo, pian pamponponan.
target_text: <MISSING_TRANSLATION>

source_text: 085<TAB>Diman so angipomponan dad kindi laki Abraham tan di asawa ran Sara; diman so angipomponan ed kindi laki Isaac tan di asawa ran Rebeca; tan diman met so angipomponan kod kinen Lea.
target_text: <MISSING_TRANSLATION>

source_text: 086<TAB>Asaliw ed saray Heteo ira may alog tan ongib.
target_text: <MISSING_TRANSLATION>

source_text: 086<TAB>Diman yo ak ipompon.
target_text: <MISSING_TRANSLATION>

source_text: 087<TAB>Kayarin binilin nen Jacob iray anak ton lalaki, pinmawil a dinmokul, insan inatey.
target_text: <MISSING_TRANSLATION>

source_text: verse<TAB>content
target_text: verse<TAB>content

source_text: 001<TAB>Intakba nen Jose so laman to ed kinen ama to, manakakis tan inaanguban tod lupa.
target_text: 001<TAB>Kinaul neng Jose i tata na; tengisan ne at penuma ne lupa.

source_text: 002<TAB>Insan to ingganggan iray aripen ton doktor ya ibalsamo ray bangkay nen ama to.
target_text: 002<TAB>Kaybat inutus na karing doktor a talasuyu na ing balsamuan de i tata na.

source_text: 003<TAB>Apataplon agew so impakaibalsamod sikato a singa pakakaibalsamod karaklan.
target_text: 002<TAB>Memintu la reti.

source_text: 003<TAB>Insan pitomplon agew ya inermenan na saray Egipsio.
target_text: 003<TAB>Apat apulung aldo ing kailangan ba reng lubus abalsamuan.

source_text: 004<TAB>Nen kayariy panaon na panagermen, inkuanen Jose ed saray opisyal na ari, No walay panagmatalek yod siak, ibaga yo pad ari,
target_text: 003<TAB>Pitung pulung aldo reng tengisan ding tau Ehipto.

source_text: 005<TAB>Nen ngalngali la ompatey so amak, impaisipan dad siak ya ipompon kod lobuk ya imparaan dad dalin na Canaan.
target_text: 004<TAB>Inyang milabas na la ding panaun na ning karelang pamagpaldas, pekisabian na lang Jose ding opisyal na ning ari.

source_text: 005<TAB>Kanyan abuloyan yo ak pan onla, ta ipompon koy amak, insan ak dia ompawil.
target_text: 004<TAB>Ngana, Nung tune yu kung kaluguran, ipakisabi kung mayap kekayu king ipayabut yu king ari ing anti kaniti para kanaku

source_text: 006<TAB>Inmebat so ari, Laka, ta ipompon moy amam onung na insipan mon gawaen.
target_text: 005<TAB>Pepasumpan na kung tata ku bayu ya mete king pakutkut ke king kutkutan a sidia na king sakup ning Canaan.

source_text: 007<TAB>Kanyan linman imponpon nen Jose so ama to.
target_text: 005<TAB>Inya aduan ku ing paintulutan yu kung adala ke at apakutkut karin i tata ku.

source_text: 007<TAB>Akilad kinen Jose iray amin ya opisyal na ari, saray lalakin atagey so kipapasen dad palasio, tan amin a manonan lalaki ed Egipto.
target_text: 005<TAB>Kaybat magbalik ku naman.

source_text: 008<TAB>Akilad sikato ray kabyangay pamilya to, saray lalakin agagi to, tan saray arum nin kabyangay pamilya nen ama to.
target_text: 006<TAB>Mekibat ya ing ari, Wa.

source_text: 008<TAB>Atilak ed dalin na Gosen iray ankekelag ya anak da, tan saray karniro, kanding, tan saray baka ra.
target_text: 006<TAB>Pakutkut me i tata mu antimo ing pengaku mu.

source_text: 009<TAB>Akila met ed sikato ray lalakin akalogan ed karwahi, tan saray akakabayo; dakerakel iran nanoolup.
target_text: 007<TAB>Meko ne i Jose ban pakutkut ne i tata na.

source_text: 010<TAB>Nen akasabi rad pasen a panagilikan diad Atad a bokig na Jordan, nanggawa ra na andokey tan maermen a sirimonyay pompon.
target_text: 007<TAB>Tikian de ring sabla nang ipus ning ari, ding opisyal na king palasyu na, at pati na ding sablang memalen a pikabaluan king Ehipto.

source_text: 010<TAB>Pitoy agew a nanggaway Jose na sirimonyay ermen.
target_text: 008<TAB>Kayabe na la namang Jose ding pamilya na, ding kapatad na, at ding aliwa pang pamilya nang tata na.

source_text: 011<TAB>Nen anengneng na saray Cananeo ira may totoon maneermen diad Atad inkuanda, Sirimonya ya na ermen da ray Egipsio.
target_text: 008<TAB>Bukud mung ding karelang anak a mangalati, ding animal a sese ra, at kawan ilang melakuan king sakup ning Gosen.

source_text: 011<TAB>Sikato yay makasengeg no akin et atawag iman a pasen na Abel-mizraim.
target_text: 009<TAB>Atin la namang kayabe paka-karwahe at pakasake kabayu.

source_text: 012<TAB>Kanyan ginawa na saray lalakin anak nen Jacob so ingganggan tod sikara
target_text: 009<TAB>Tutu lang dakal ding tinuki kang Jose.

source_text: 013<TAB>inyakar dad Canaan so bangkay to, imponpon dad ongib ed Macpela a bokig na Mamre, diad samay alog a sinaliw nen Abraham ed kinen Efron a Heteo, ta ginawa ton pasen a pomponan.
target_text: 010<TAB>Inyang miras la king pidadaran karin Atad a atyu sumangid ning Jordan, karin la menangis at tutung makaba at kapait-paitan ing panagulele ra.

source_text: 014<TAB>Kayarin nipompon nen Jose so bangkay nen ama to, pinmawil ed Egipto a kaiba to ray lalakin agagi to tan amin ya akilad sikaton akitolur.
target_text: 010<TAB>Pitu neng aldo penangisan Jose i tata na.

source_text: 015<TAB>Kayariy impatey nen ama ra, inkuan na lalakin agagi nen Jose, Nayarin bosulen itayo ni nen Jose tan mamplanon ombawid sikatayon amin, lapud samay ginawa tayod sikato.
target_text: 011<TAB>Ikit da ring Cananeong manuknangan karin ing pamanagulele ra king pidadaran king Atad.

source_text: 016<TAB>Kanyan impaikuan dad kinen Jose, Kasakbayan ya inatey si ama tayo,
target_text: 011<TAB>Ngara, Kapait-paitan ing pamanaguleleng gagawan da reting tau Ehipto.

source_text: 017<TAB>impaikuandad sika, Pirdonam pa la ray agagim a lalaki ed samay kasalanan a ginawa rad sika.
target_text: 011<TAB>Inya inaus deng Abel-mizraim ing lugal a ita.

source_text: 017<TAB>Pirdona mo kami pa la sirin natan ed samay kaogsan a ginawa mi, sikamin aripen na Dios nen amam.
target_text: 011<TAB>Atyu sumangid na ning Jordan.

source_text: 017<TAB>Inmakis si Jose nen nadngel to yan impaibaga ra.
target_text: 012<TAB>Makanyan dang tiparan ding anak nang Jacob ing penabilin na karela.

source_text: 018<TAB>Insan saray agagi ton dili so dinmago tan dinmakmomo rad sikato.
target_text: 013<TAB>Dela re ding anak na king sakup ning Canaan at pepakutkut de king kueba king marangle karin Makpela, king dane nang aslagan ning Mamre, ketang gabun a seli nang Abraham kang Efron a Hiteo, ing gabun a gewa nang pikutkutan.

source_text: 018<TAB>Inkuanda, Nia kami ran aripen mo.
target_text: 014<TAB>Kaybat nang mikutkut tata na, mibalik ya Ehipto i Jose; kayabe na la ding kapatad na at ding tinuking mekipangutkut kang tata na.

source_text: 019<TAB>Balet inkuanen Jose ed sikara, Ag kayo natatakot; ag ko nayarian ya alaey pasen na Dios.
target_text: 015<TAB>Inyang mikutkut ne i tata ra, dinalan king lub da ring kapatad na ing panamdam a maki mua ya pa karela i Jose at mablas ya karela ketang e mayap a depat da kang Jose.

source_text: 020<TAB>Nankokomplutan yo ak a nanggawaay maoges, balet say Dios impagmaliw to a pankaabigan iman a kaogsan, pian makapambilay iray amayamay a totoo, saray totoon mabilay natan lapud saman ya agawa.
target_text: 016<TAB>Inya ngarang pepasabi kang Jose, Bayu ya mete i tatang pepasabi na king

source_text: 021<TAB>Anggapoy nepeg yon takotan.
target_text: 017<TAB>patawaran mu na sana ing depat ming kasalanan keka, ikaming kapatad mu.

source_text: 021<TAB>Asikasoen ta kayo tan saray anak yo.
target_text: 017<TAB>Inya ngeni ipakisabi mi sana patawaran mu na kami king lagyu na ning Dios nang tatang.

source_text: 021<TAB>Onya so impamabiskeg toy linawa ra tan impanligliwa tod sikara.
target_text: 017<TAB>Mipakiak ya i Jose king sinabi ra ding kapatad na.

source_text: 022<TAB>Kaiba nen Jose a nanayam ed Egipto iray kabyangay pamilya nen ama to; sanlasus tan samploray taon to nen inatey.
target_text: 018<TAB>Lepitan de ring kapatad na at migsakab la arapan na.

source_text: 023<TAB>Naalagar to nin anengneng iray anak nen Efraim tan saray apo tod sikato.
target_text: 018<TAB>Ngara, Makasadia kaming maging ipus mu!

source_text: 023<TAB>Mabilay ni nen naawat a kabyangan na pamilya to iray anak nen Makir, say lakin anak nen Manases.
target_text: 019<TAB>Pekibat nang Jose karela, E kayu tatakut.

source_text: 024<TAB>Inkuantod saray lalakin agagi to, Ngalngali ak la ompatey, balet andi-saew ya asikasoen kayo na Dios, tan ipaway to kayod sayan dalin tan iyakar to kayod dalin a sinambaan ton iter ed kindi Abraham, Isaac, tan Jacob.
target_text: 019<TAB>Dios ku wari?

source_text: 025<TAB>Insan kinerew tod saray totoo to a sambaan dan gawaen yan bilin to.
target_text: 020<TAB>E mayap ing tingka yu laban kanaku, oneng mayap ing inalili na kaniti ning Dios ban dakal la ring taung miligtas antimo ing milyari.

source_text: 025<TAB>Inkuanto, Isipan yod siak a no say Dios et iyakar to kayod saman a dalin, piawit yo ray pokel ko.
target_text: 021<TAB>E kayu tatakut; e ra kayu paburen pati na ding anak yu.

source_text: 026<TAB>Kanyan inatey si Jose nen mantaoy sanlasus tan samplora.
target_text: 021<TAB>Makanyan na lang leko karug salu at pematulan.

source_text: 026<TAB>Imbalsamo rad Egipto, insan da inkargad longun.
target_text: 022<TAB>Mibiebie ya Ehipto i Jose at ding kapatad na.

source_text: <MISSING_TRANSLATION>
target_text: 022<TAB>Disnan na ing dinalan at apulung banua.

source_text: <MISSING_TRANSLATION>
target_text: 023<TAB>Ikit na la pa ding anak nang Efraim angga king katlung lahi; antimu rin ding anak nang Makir a anak nang Manase.

source_text: <MISSING_TRANSLATION>
target_text: 023<TAB>Ikit na la pang Jose inyang mibait la.

source_text: <MISSING_TRANSLATION>
target_text: 024<TAB>Nganang Jose karing kapatad na, Malapit na kung mate.

source_text: <MISSING_TRANSLATION>
target_text: 024<TAB>Pero e na kayu paburen ning Dios.

source_text: <MISSING_TRANSLATION>
target_text: 024<TAB>Ilual na kayu king bansang iti at idala king gabun a pengaku na kang Abraham, Isaac, at Jacob.

source_text: <MISSING_TRANSLATION>
target_text: 025<TAB>Kanita pepangakuanan na la ring anak nang Israel.

source_text: <MISSING_TRANSLATION>
target_text: 025<TAB>Ngana, Potang dalawan na kayu ning Dios at ilual king lugal a iti, idala yu la ring kanakung butul.

source_text: <MISSING_TRANSLATION>
target_text: 026<TAB>Mete ya i Jose inyang dinalan ya at apulung banua.

source_text: <MISSING_TRANSLATION>
target_text: 026<TAB>Binalsamuan de at binili re king metung a kabaung karin king Ehipto.
